      "{image 15}\n– Yesterday we were sitting in the backyard, listening to their music. There was a fly that first flew to your ankle and then to my knee. We were very rich, we had so much green. You were drinking juice and then I died.",
      "{image 21}",
      "{image 16}\n– peruna, porkkana, lanttu, soijanakkeja (kahta erilaista), kasvisliemikuutio, kokonaisia mustapippureita, persilja, vessapaperi, ruisleipää, sinappia, olutta, sipsiä, hammaslankaa (littanaa),",
