    "shortDescription": "I found a mouth and fell into it is a solo performance for a restless mouth. A mouth that whispers, cries, sighs, rests, talks, hesitates, licks, laughs, whistles, spits, repeats, mumbles, interrupts, murmurs, pauses. Th",
    "fullDescription": [
      "I found a mouth and fell into it",
      "2019\nperformance\n30 min",
      "{image 17}",
      "… and I answered: “Yes Mom, I know. I have swallowed \nall the birds, butterflies \nand \nairplanes. \nShhhh, shhhh, shhhh.",
      "I found a mouth and fell into it is a solo performance for a restless mouth. A mouth that whispers, cries, sighs, rests, talks, hesitates, licks, laughs, whistles, spits, repeats, mumbles, interrupts, murmurs, pauses. The performance is a trial to live with the drama of the mouth and to rearrange memories, fantasies and struggles through voicing and mouthing.",
      "Performances\nCOMA, The Center of Multisensory Arts, STPLN, Malmö, Sweden\nSeven of seven  performance festival, Myymälä2 Gallery, Helsinki, Finalnd. ",
      "The work is supported by COMA, The Center of Multisensory Arts."
    ],
    "contentHtml": "<b>I found a mouth and fell into it</b><br />\r\n<br />\r\n2019<br />\r\nperformance<br />\r\n30 min<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"assets/projects/i-found-a-mouth-and-fell-into-it/01.jpg\" width=\"670\" height=\"1071\" width_o=\"2399\" height_o=\"3838\" src_o=\"assets/projects/i-found-a-mouth-and-fell-into-it/01.jpg\" data-mid=\"77349371\" border=\"0\" align=\"left\" data-title=\"670 — 670 × 1071\"data-hi-res=\"assets/projects/i-found-a-mouth-and-fell-into-it/01.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<i>… and I answered: “Yes Mom, I know. I have swallowed <br />\r\nall the birds, butterflies <br />\r\nand <br />\r\nairplanes. <br />\r\nShhhh, shhhh, shhhh.</i><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<i>I found a mouth and fell into it</i> is a solo performance for a restless mouth. A mouth that whispers, cries, sighs, rests, talks, hesitates, licks, laughs, whistles, spits, repeats, mumbles, interrupts, murmurs, pauses. The performance is a trial to live with the drama of the mouth and to rearrange memories, fantasies and struggles through voicing and mouthing.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<b>Performances</b><br />\r\nCOMA, The Center of Multisensory Arts, STPLN, Malmö, Sweden<br />\r\n<i>Seven of seven </i> performance festival, Myymälä2 Gallery, Helsinki, Finalnd. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe work is supported by COMA, The Center of Multisensory Arts.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n",
    "contentText": "I found a mouth and fell into it\n\n2019\nperformance\n30 min\n\n{image 17}\n\n… and I answered: “Yes Mom, I know. I have swallowed \nall the birds, butterflies \nand \nairplanes. \nShhhh, shhhh, shhhh.\n\nI found a mouth and fell into it is a solo performance for a restless mouth. A mouth that whispers, cries, sighs, rests, talks, hesitates, licks, laughs, whistles, spits, repeats, mumbles, interrupts, murmurs, pauses. The performance is a trial to live with the drama of the mouth and to rearrange memories, fantasies and struggles through voicing and mouthing.\n\nPerformances\nCOMA, The Center of Multisensory Arts, STPLN, Malmö, Sweden\nSeven of seven  performance festival, Myymälä2 Gallery, Helsinki, Finalnd. \n\nThe work is supported by COMA, The Center of Multisensory Arts.",
