    "contentText": "WATER FALL 4 \n\n2017\nPerformance (30 min)\nInstallation \n with Maarit Mustonen\n\n{image 11}\n\nWATER FALL 4 at B-galleria, Turku, 8–9 June 2017.\n\nWATER FALL, a 7-part body of work, was based on our shared interest in memory, imagination and the liquid quality of language and body. The work consisted of performances and installations that we presented in 2016-2018 in galleries and performance art spaces. The elements of the previous part always flowed and influenced the next part. Over the years, the embodied working process explored themes such as commitment, metamorphosis and friendship.\n\n{image 13}{image 9}{image 8}{image 7}{image 6} Images: Henna Kukkonen",
